{"title":"西行剪影","authors":["张志民"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":1,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"西行剪影"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张志民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋到葡萄沟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋到葡萄沟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"珠宝满沟流，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亭亭座座珍珠塔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"层层叠叠翡翠楼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"轻走些！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“玫瑰紫”刚刚吃醉酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"且留神！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小心“马奶子”蹭身油！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞧！车车马马哪里去？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葡萄公社庆丰收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听！园林深处什么响？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一曲情歌拂绿洲。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葡萄沟呵，葡萄沟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葡萄沟横抹千山秀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葡萄沟呵，葡萄沟！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尝一颗葡萄心甜透。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风吹碧浪香千里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"葡萄沟风光瞧不够！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枝枝蔓蔓多情带，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"缠住我心儿不让走……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和田即景"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和田——丝、玉之乡，地毯之乡，花果之乡，歌舞之乡……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——摘自日记"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"窗前苹果窗后桃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河底美玉信手捞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"桑间柳辫飞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"田头牛鼓敲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩裙翩翩街头舞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鲜花片片小河漂……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"歌声迎日起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玉笛伴霞落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜半灯火枝头红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"明月窗前身影摇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"谁道姑娘忙织毯？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在为和田织新貌……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登天池"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"躬身敲海磬，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举臂扣天环，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月在手上托，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"云在脚下缠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"银镜横映瑶台雪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是天上呵，是人间？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问戈壁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问草原——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪代能人夺天巧？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一块碧玉嵌九天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侧耳听牧笛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬眼望炊烟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雁传果花香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风送毡房暖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千尺彩波金杯酒，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牧民乐呵，猎户欢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"霞在怀中落，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"星在怀中闪——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酒艳花香今欲醉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"喜举金杯唱天山……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}